contentrichtext.text: '''Umpqua''' may refer to: ; a placename in the U.S. state of Oregon * [[Umpqua, Oregon]], a community * Umpqua City, Oregon, the former name of [[Winchester Bay, Oregon]] * [[Umpqua Community College]] * [[Umpqua County, Oregon]], a former county * [[Umpqua Hot Springs]] * [[Umpqua National Forest]] * [[Umpqua River]] * [[Umpqua River Light]] * [[Umpqua Valley AVA]], a wine growing region ; a group of people * [[Umpqua (tribe)]], any of several distinct groups of Native Americans that live in present-day south central Oregon, United States ; a business * [[Umpqua Holdings Corporation]] (NASDAQ: UMPQ) {{disambig}}
